  StyleBox[
   RowBox[{"Z", "Z", "Z"}], "TI"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontSize->0.9 Inherited,ExpressionUUID->
  "0c479268-3713-4892-b3ea-7721d66135db"],
 ", the conserved parity that binds the three ",
